{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a pencil-sketched character and journey through hand-drawn levels in this story-based platformer. Explore sketches, paintings, and diary entries to reveal the story of one ordinary man\u2019s life through the 80s, 90s, 00s and up to the modern era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/extras/Drawn_Before_forest_hill.gif?t=1736535587\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A narrative-based, single player adventure with a focus on environmental variety, story, and challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple and intuitive controls - move, jump, dash, and a few other surprises here and there.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Regular checkpoints throughout areas, with instant respawns. Game saves at the start of each new level.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/extras/ogre_boss_vid.gif?t=1736535587\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Zero skill-trees, unlockables, or purchasable items. Just raw, honest platforming (with the occasional power up of course).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original music, composed with care for each level of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736535587","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736535587","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329490/c9df268dfbf44fd838690982f4b30ff196a23b95/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736535587","capsule_imagev5":"https://shar